Class AntiTheftPreferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.innolabs.spydroid.AntiTheftPreferences

  • public class AntiTheftPreferences
extends Activity
    Activity to show the Anti-Theft Preferences. This window displays the Settings or Preferences for the Anti-Theft module which is installed on the device.
    Version:
    1.03
    Author:
    Srikanth Rao
